Package: rmRNAseq
Type: Package
Title: RNA-seq Analysis for Repeated-measures Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Yet Nguyen <tienyettoan@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Yet Nguyen <tienyettoan@gmail.com>
Description: This package implements a differential expression analysis for RNA-seq data from repeated-measures design using general linear model framework and parametric bootstrap inference. 
